---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="BRICS Brokers | 全球及新兴市场准入"
  description="为寻求超越传统边界的客户构建简单、透明、合规的准入路径。在基里巴斯共和国注册。"
  lang="zh"
>
  <Fragment slot="logo">BRICS Brokers</Fragment>
  <Fragment slot="footer-name">BRICS Brokers – 在基里巴斯共和国注册</Fragment>

  <section class="bb-hero">
    <div class="bb-hero-bg"></div>
    <div class="bb-hero-overlay"></div>
    <div class="bb-hero-content">
      <h1 class="bb-title">The BRICS Brokers</h1>
      <p class="bb-tagline">创业级全球及新兴市场准入。</p>
      <p class="bb-lead">为寻求超越传统边界的客户构建简单、透明、合规的准入路径。</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="ad-slot">广告位 - Google AdSense</div>

  <div class="card-grid">
    <article class="card">
      <h2>快速入驻</h2>
      <p>专为速度和清晰度设计的精简流程。联系我们，确定您的需求，完成身份和资格审查，然后开始运营并获得持续支持。</p>
    </article>
    <article class="card">
      <h2>全球视野</h2>
      <p>专注于新兴和非传统市场。外汇和宏观环境、大宗商品、股票指数和数字资产（视情况而定）。</p>
    </article>
    <article class="card">
      <h2>透明结构</h2>
      <p>清晰的工作流程，没有隐藏层。流程的每一步都以透明度和合规性为核心。</p>
    </article>
    <article class="card">
      <h2>人工支持</h2>
      <p>直接联系，真实的人。我们的团队在您进入全球市场的整个过程中提供个性化帮助。</p>
    </article>
    <article class="card">
      <h2>市场准入与执行</h2>
      <p>通过可靠的执行基础设施进入全球和新兴市场。客户入驻、报告和洞察——不提供财务建议。</p>
    </article>
    <article class="card">
      <h2>合规优先</h2>
      <p>所有服务均在合规导向的框架内提供，根据司法管辖区和客户概况进行资格审查。</p>
    </article>
  </div>

  <div class="ad-slot">广告位 - Google AdSense</div>

  <section class="registration-info">
    <h2>注册与法律信息</h2>
    <p><strong>注册号：</strong> CP-000024</p>
    <p><strong>许可证号：</strong> KBN-90-000002</p>
    <p><strong>地址：</strong> Central Build, Tarawa, 基里巴斯共和国</p>
  </section>

  <div class="ad-slot">广告位 - Google AdSense</div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .bb-hero {
    position: relative;
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    overflow: hidden;
    margin: -40px -20px 0;
    padding: 0;
  }
  .bb-hero-bg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background-image: url('/images/bricsbrother.webp');
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center;
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
  }
  .bb-hero-overlay {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(
      180deg,
      rgba(0,0,0,.55) 0%,
      rgba(0,0,0,.7) 50%,
      rgba(0,0,0,.85) 100%
    );
  }
  .bb-hero-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 800px;
    padding: 40px 24px;
  }
  .bb-title {
    font-size: 4rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #fff;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    text-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,.5);
    letter-spacing: -.02em;
    line-height: 1.1;
  }
  .bb-tagline {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,.95);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    text-shadow: 0 2px 10px rgba(0,0,0,.4);
  }
  .bb-lead {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,.8);
    line-height: 1.7;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-shadow: 0 1px 6px rgba(0,0,0,.3);
  }
  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .bb-title { font-size: 2.4rem; }
    .bb-tagline { font-size: 1.1rem; }
    .bb-lead { font-size: 1rem; }
  }
  .registration-info {
    background: white;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 32px;
    margin-top: 32px;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
    text-align: center;
  }
  .registration-info h2 {
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    color: #1a1a2e;
  }
  .registration-info p {
    margin: 6px 0;
    color: #555;
  }
</style>
